cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CR 

The paper deals with computer vision and robotics, specifically in the context of autonomous vehicles. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of machine learning algorithms, which suggests the category cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also discusses the use of ROS (Robot Operating System), which is a popular platform for robotics research, indicating the category cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also involves the use of deep learning algorithms, which suggests the category cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper discusses the issue of safety in autonomous vehicles, which suggests the category cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
